The paper deals with the stylization of fluid simulations using neural networks, which involves computer graphics (cs.GR) and computer vision (cs.CV) techniques. The authors also mention the use of machine learning (cs.AI) and image processing (cs.MM) methods. Additionally, the paper involves the manipulation of 3D shapes (cs.CG).
